sub_title: Lecturer at College of Natural Resources, Programme Leader for BSc. Agriculture, Agronomy, Crop Science and Physiology, System Analysis
summary: Hello! I'm an accomplished Associate Lecturer at the Royal University of Bhutan's College of Natural Resources, where I've dedicated the past 7 years to fostering education and innovation. Holding a Master's degree in Plant Science with a specialization in Crop Science from Wageningen University and Research, my passion lies in cultivating knowledge and cultivating crops. As the Programme Leader of the BSc. Agriculture programme, I've embraced the dual role of educator and researcher. Join me in exploring the fascinating world of agricultural science and its boundless possibilities.
